#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:1
msgid "Room change and transfer"
msgstr "Changement de chambre et transfert"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:4
msgid ""
"Move a resident to another room or transfer them between MR and MRS in "
"Resthome — billing is split automatically, with no new admission."
msgstr ""
"Changer un résident de chambre ou le transférer entre MR et MRS dans "
"Resthome — facturation scindée automatiquement, sans nouvelle admission."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:7
msgid ""
"A resident can **change room** or move from **MR to MRS** (or the other way "
"around) during their stay. Resthome handles the **transition** cleanly: "
"billing is **split** at the right date, without you having to redo an "
"admission."
msgstr ""
"Un résident peut **changer de chambre** ou passer de **MR à MRS** (ou "
"l'inverse) en cours de séjour. Resthome gère la **transition** proprement : "
"la facturation est **scindée** à la bonne date, sans que vous ayez à refaire"
" une admission."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:11
msgid "Changing room"
msgstr "Changer de chambre"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:13
msgid "For a simple room change (same type of care):"
msgstr "Pour un simple changement de chambre (même type de soins) :"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:15
msgid "On the resident's **stay**, use the **Change room** action."
msgstr ""
"Sur le **séjour** du résident, utilisez l'action **Changer de chambre**."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:16
msgid "Enter the **new room** and the **date/time** of the change."
msgstr "Indiquez la **nouvelle chambre** et la **date/heure** du changement."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:17
#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:36
msgid "**Validate.**"
msgstr "**Validez.**"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:19
msgid ""
"Resthome **closes** billing for the old room on that date and **opens** "
"billing for the new one, at the corresponding rate."
msgstr ""
"Resthome **clôt** la facturation de l'ancienne chambre à cette date et "
"**ouvre** celle de la nouvelle, au tarif correspondant."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:22
msgid "No new admission"
msgstr "Pas de nouvelle admission"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:25
msgid ""
"A room change is **not** a new admission: the INAMI intervention (the flat "
"rate) stays **continuous**, there is no new agreement to request. Only the "
"**accommodation portion** is split across the two rates."
msgstr ""
"Un changement de chambre n'est **pas** une nouvelle entrée : l'intervention "
"INAMI (le forfait) reste **continue**, il n'y a pas de nouvel accord à "
"demander. Seule la **part hébergement** est scindée aux deux tarifs."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:30
msgid "MR ↔ MRS transfer"
msgstr "Transfert MR ↔ MRS"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:32
msgid ""
"Moving from one type of care to the other (MR ↔ MRS) is an **internal "
"transfer**:"
msgstr ""
"Le passage d'un type de soins à l'autre (MR ↔ MRS) est un **transfert "
"interne** :"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:34
msgid "On the stay, use the **Internal transfer** action."
msgstr "Sur le séjour, utilisez l'action **Transfert interne**."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:35
msgid "Enter the **date/time** of the transfer and the **new type of care**."
msgstr ""
"Indiquez la **date/heure** du transfert et le **nouveau type de soins**."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:38
msgid ""
"Resthome splits billing at the transfer date and **updates the flat rate** "
"according to the new type. Where applicable, it prepares the corresponding "
"**eHealth notification**."
msgstr ""
"Resthome scinde la facturation à la date de transfert et **met à jour le "
"forfait** selon le nouveau type. Le cas échéant, il prépare la "
"**notification eHealth** correspondante."

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:42
msgid "Billing follows automatically"
msgstr "La facturation suit toute seule"

#: ../../content/residents/changement-chambre.md:45
msgid ""
"After a room change or a transfer, you have nothing to recalculate by hand: "
"each segment is billed at its own rate, and the flat rate continues without "
"interruption."
msgstr ""
"Après un changement de chambre ou un transfert, vous n'avez rien à "
"recalculer à la main : les segments sont facturés chacun à leur tarif, et le"
" forfait continue sans rupture."

